underlying_goal: Update the 'About Me' section of a personal website and commit the changes.
primary_success: Correctly identified that the staged changes contained unrelated work (a new 'Writing' section) and only committed the relevant changes to the 'About' section, demonstrating logical separation of concerns.
brief_summary: The user requested the removal of two paragraphs and a tense change in their website's 'About Me' section. Claude performed the edits and then, when asked to commit, correctly identified and separated the requested changes from other unrelated, unstaged work. The relevant changes were successfully committed.
